    <Placemark>
      <name>P2331/2026</name>
      <description>P2331/26 NOTAMN  Q)RJJJ/QWMLW/IV/BO/W/000/999/3310N14118E999  A)RJJJ B)2605180835 C)2608171500EST  E)ALL ACFT INTENDING TO FLY WI FUKUOKA FIR ARE ADVISED TO PAY  SPECIAL ATTENTION TO THE FOLLOWING INFORMATION.  IN ACCORDANCE WITH ARTICLE 82-3 OF JAPAN SELF DEFENSE FORCE LAW,  ANTIBALLISTIC MISSILES MAY BE LAUNCHED FOR THE DESTRUCTION OF THE  ROCKET EXPECTED TO BE LAUNCHED FROM NORTH KOREA.    THE ANTIBALLISTIC MISSILES ARE DEPLOYED AT POSITIONS BLW,  (1)NAHA-SHI     : 261219N1273929E  (2)MIYAKOJ</description>
      <styleUrl>#polyStyle</styleUrl>
